      <textblock>
        Patients with chronic hepatitis delta will be screened regardless of HDV or HBV genotype
      </textblock>
    </study_pop>
    <sampling_method>Non-Probability Sample</sampling_method>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

        • Positive HBs antigen and antiHDV for longer than 6 months.

